          'Promoted to lead a talented Customer Success Manager team, partnering with customers to drive product adoption and utilisation. Ensured they exceeded their goals. Awarded CS Leader of the Quarter - Q1 2022.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Senior Security Program Manager',
        start_date: 'May 2021',
        end_date: 'May 2021',
        description: null,
      },
      {
        title: 'Security Program Manager',
        start_date: 'March 2020',
        end_date: 'May 2021',
        description:
          'Responsible for the success, renewal & growth of a strategic portfolio of EMEA customers. Provided high-touch account management for Fortune 500 companies. Exceeded renewal & expansion KPIs. Awarded Best Newcomer in EMEA 2020 & CSM of the Quarter Q2 2021.',
      },
    ],
  },
  {
    company: 'Lacework',
    location: 'London, England, United Kingdom',
    roles: [
      {
        title: 'Senior Customer Success Manager',
        start_date: 'April 2022',
